1. install the gem by gem install daily-reporter
2. copy settings.yml.sample to settings.yml and set your credentials
3. add the task by daily-reporter task add 'task description'
   you can look through the task lists by daily-reporter task list
4. get the email to respond
5. run daily-reporter report to send the report
   tasks list will be cleaned

